    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 chassis. This vehicle is powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical provenance is impeccable: the dual-VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure long-term structural integrity. Suspension kinematics remain factory-sharp, complemented by a limited-slip differential that provides exceptional lock-up under lateral load. The paint exhibits zero swirl marks or rock chips, reflecting a climate-controlled life, while the undercarriage remains free of any electrolytic corrosion. This is a turn-key, concours-level machine for the discerning purist.",
